Revision history for perl script mbserverd


1.6.1 2015-12-03

     - Change signals handlers for compatibility with supervisor.

1.6.0 2015-11-26

     - Non-root users can now launch mbserverd if bind to tcp port >= 1024.
     - Set unbuffered mode for STDOUT/STDERR.
     - Default PID file /var/run/mbserverd.pid is set only for root daemon mode.

1.5.0 2015-11-26

     - Add "-n" option to launch script in the foreground (nodaemon option).

1.4.0 2015-11-26

     - Add "-p" option to change default TCP port to listening.

1.3.0 2013-03-10

     - Code and comment is now in english (more easy to share).

